<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-39-0517 </DOCNO><TEXT>Today, highly frequent radio waves are regarded as undangerous to man.Diseases seen at radar-technicians during the 2nd World War, however,indicated that microwaves applied in radar systems were hazardous tohealth. The Russian work medicine has been knowing microwave-caused hazardsin industry since the beginning of the thirties. Therefore in some East-Europeancountries there are terms of protection and severe norms of safety forthe staying of persons in the radiation sphere of microwaves.</TEXT></DOC>